# Expert Strategy: Vivek Goel (Enterprise SaaS & ABM)

**Focus:** Pipeline Velocity & 2026 Algorithmic Optimization  
**Core Thesis:** In high-ACV B2B sales, virality is a distraction. Use LinkedIn as an orchestration layer for Account-Based Marketing (ABM) to nurture the 6–10 stakeholders in a buying committee.

---

