## 3. Content Format Engagement Benchmarks (2026)
Format selection is a technical constraint that dictates reach.

| Content Format | Avg. Engagement Rate | Reach Multiplier | Primary Benefit |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Document/Carousel (PDF)** | **6.60%** | **5.0x clicks** | Highest dwell time; signals high value. |
| **Native Video (Short)** | 4.25% | 1.44x reach | Authentic storytelling and trust. |
| **Text-Only with Hook** | 3.10% | Variable | Low friction; personal insight. |
| **Polls and Questions** | 2.80% | High interaction | Audience research and feedback loops. |

